==直立人==
{{further|阿舍利}}
[[更新世|更新世]]時，南亞的[[直立人|直立人]]（''Homo erectus''）存在於[[波特瓦尔高原|波特瓦尔高原]]（今巴基斯坦[[旁遮普省|旁遮普省]]北部）[[索安河|索安河]]流域。[[西瓦利克山脈|西瓦利克地區]]現在還有許多直立人化石點。<ref>Parth R. Chauhan. [http://www.assemblage.group.shef.ac.uk/issue7/chauhan.html#distribution Distribution of Acheulian sites in the Siwalik region] {{Wayback|url=http://www.assemblage.group.shef.ac.uk/issue7/chauhan.html#distribution |date=20120104171240 }}. ''An Overview of the Siwalik Acheulian & Reconsidering Its Chronological Relationship with the Soanian – A Theoretical Perspective''.</ref> 他們已經開始使用雙面石斧和石刀{{sfn|Kennedy|2000|p=136}}，[[阿舍利|阿舍利]]也出現于這一時期。{{sfn|Kennedy|2000|p=160}}

==智人==
[[粒線體DNA|粒線體DNA]]研究表明南亞[[早期人類遷徙|早期智人遷徙]]出現在75,000至50,000年前<ref>{{cite book|author=Alice Roberts|date=2010|title=The Incredible Human Journey|publisher=A&C Black|page=90}}</ref>{{sfn|James|Petraglia|2005|loc=S6}}。對[[Y染色體|Y染色體]][[單倍群|單倍群]]的研究顯示今[[马杜赖|马杜赖]]東部一村莊的居民是這些移民的直系後裔<ref>Spencer Wells, The Journey of Man: A Genetic Odyssey. Random House, ISBN 0-8129-7146-9</ref>。 創造了[[比莫貝特卡石窟|比莫貝特卡石窟]]（歷史可追溯至前30,000年）的人類一直生活到前一萬至八千年的[[舊石器時代晚期|舊石器時代晚期]]。<ref>{{cite book|title=The Hindus: An Alternative History|page=66|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=nNsXZkdHvXUC|author=[[Wendy_Doniger|Wendy Doniger]]|publisher=Oxford University Press|isbn=9780199593347|date=2010-09-30|access-date=2016-11-30|archive-date=2020-08-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200802015701/https://books.google.com/books?id=nNsXZkdHvXUC|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|title=Architecture of First Societies: A Global Perspective|page=62|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=DuevAwAAQBAJ|author=Mark M. Jarzombek|publisher=John Wiley & Sons|isbn=9781118421055|date=2014-05-27|access-date=2016-11-30|archive-date=2020-08-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200802015706/https://books.google.com/books?id=DuevAwAAQBAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Archaeological Survey of India|first=Government of India|title=World Heritage Sites - Rock Shelters of Bhimbetka|url=http://asi.nic.in/asi_monu_whs_rockart_bhimbetka.asp|publisher=Archaeological Survey of India, Government of India|accessdate=4 March 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140327162814/http://asi.nic.in/asi_monu_whs_rockart_bhimbetka.asp|archive-date=2014-03-27|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

==新石器時代==

以巴基斯坦[[梅赫爾格爾|梅赫爾格爾]]為代表的南亞新石器時代無陶階段出現在前7000至5500年，有陶階段則延續至前3300年，繼之以早期哈拉帕文明。印度較早的新石器時代遺址發現于[[聖卡比爾那加爾縣|聖卡比爾那加爾縣]]的“Lahuradewa”和[[安拉阿巴德縣|安拉阿巴德縣]][[久西|久西]]，均可追溯至前7000年<ref>{{cite journal |last=Fuller |first=Dorian |date=2006 |title=Agricultural Origins and Frontiers in South Asia: A Working Synthesis |url=http://www.homepages.ucl.ac.uk/~tcrndfu/articles/JWP20.pdf |journal=Journal of World Prehistory |volume=20 |page=42 |doi=10.1007/s10963-006-9006-8 |access-date=2016-11-30 |archive-date=2011-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110517050130/http://www.homepages.ucl.ac.uk/~tcrndfu/articles/JWP20.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>Tewari, Rakesh et al. 2006. "Second Preliminary Report of the excavations at Lahuradewa,District Sant Kabir Nagar, UP 2002-2003-2004 & 2005-06" in Pragdhara No. 16 [http://www.uparchaeology.org/pragdhara%20No-16.pdf "Electronic Version p.28"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.uparchaeology.org/pragdhara%20No-16.pdf |date=20071128194547 }}</ref>，[[薩拉斯瓦蒂河|薩拉斯瓦蒂河]]流域的[[比拉纳|比拉纳]]化石遺址更可以追溯到前7600年<ref name="oldest">{{cite web | title=Haryana's Bhirrana oldest Harappan site, Rakhigarhi Asia's largest: ASI | url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/chandigarh/Haryanas-Bhirrana-oldest-Harappan-site-Rakhigarhi-Asias-largest-ASI/articleshow/46926693.cms | newspaper=Times of India | date=15 April 2015 | accessdate=2016-11-30 | archive-date=2016-01-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160101032332/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/chandigarh/Haryanas-Bhirrana-oldest-Harappan-site-Rakhigarhi-Asias-largest-ASI/articleshow/46926693.cms | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

南印度的新石器時代開始較晚，出現在前3000年，延續至前1400年。[[安得拉邦|安得拉]]-[[卡纳塔克邦|卡纳塔克邦]]的新石器時代文明始于前2500年，後來擴張到[[泰米尔纳德邦|泰米尔纳德邦]]地區。而泰米尔纳德邦[[蒂魯內爾維利縣|蒂魯內爾維利縣]]的“Adichanallur”和北印度的比較研究顯示，前者文明可能來自後者<ref>{{cite book |first=Kallidaikurichi Aiyah Nilakanta |last=Sastri |title=A History of South India |publisher=Oxford University Press |pages=49–51 |isbn=0-19-560686-8}}</ref>。泰米尔纳德的[[巨石文明|巨石文明]]出現在前1000年左右<ref>{{cite news |last=Subramanian |first=T. S. |date=2004-05-26 |title=Skeletons, script found at ancient burial site in Tamil Nadu |url=http://www.hindu.com/2004/05/26/stories/2004052602871200.htm |newspaper=The Hindu |accessdate=2007-07-31 |archive-date=2004-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040701084804/http://www.hindu.com/2004/05/26/stories/2004052602871200.htm |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |quote=The most interesting pre-historic remains in Tamil India were discovered at Adichanallur. There is a series of urn burials. seem to be related to the megalithic complex. |last=Zvelebil |first=Kamil A. |title=Companion Studies to the History of Tamil Literature |pages=21–22 |publisher=Brill Academic Publishers |year=1992 |isbn=90-04-09365-6}}</ref>。

